The paper proposes techniques for tail averaging in a streaming setting, which is a common problem in machine learning and data analysis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves algorithms and data structures, which suggests categories such as cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper's focus on streaming data and time series analysis suggests categories such as cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
